        <item>
            <title>Tesla Model 3 後輪驅動版抵港，一換一售價 27 萬全稅豁免 + 8 吋後排顯示</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/14/tesla-model-3-rw/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=tesla-model-3-rw</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/14/tesla-model-3-rw/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 06:20:14 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽車科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Tesla]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Tesla Model 3]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Tesla Model 3 Rear Wheel]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Tesla Model 3 RW]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1224198</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>2024-2025 年度《財政預算案》宣佈延長電動車首次登記稅寬減安排期。在新「一換一」計劃下，若購入之電動車價值不超過 HK$270,348，則無需要為電動車的首次登記繳付稅款。今日 Tesla 就宣佈推出 Tesla Model 3 Rear-Wheel Drive 後輪驅動版電動車，以新「一換一」計劃計算後售價為 270,200 港幣，可以完全享有「一換一」的全額首次登記稅寬減。今日 Tesla 就邀請了小編去看看 Tesla Model 3 Rear-Wheel Drive，現在就讓小編和大家分享這款 Tesla 的新電動車。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1224203" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0426-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0426-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0426.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1224204" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0429-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0429-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0429.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1224205" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0430-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0430-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0430.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1224206" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0432-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0432-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0432.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1224222" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0492-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0492-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0492.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>全新 8 吋後排座椅顯示螢幕讓後座乘客可以享受溫度控制、音樂播放等功能。其中內置 Netflix、YouTube 等，更可以玩遊戲。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1224211" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0442-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0442-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0442.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲後排也可控制溫度</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1224215" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0456-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0456-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0456.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲內置 Netflix、YouTube 等</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1224213" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0448-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0448-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0448.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可觀看 YouTube</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1224212" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0444-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0444-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0444.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1224214" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0450-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0450-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0450.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可播放 YouTube 影片</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1224216" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0457-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0457-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0457.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲也可看 Netflix</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1224218" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0460-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0460-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0460.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲音樂播放功能</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1224219" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0461-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_0461-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk